{"tid":266128,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Google工程師都住128呎「劏房」 八萬蚊有得找！","createTime":"2017-06-01T08:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T17:42:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"664953aabc1bfb6f182a2f23b916b751fc77ee22","tid":266128,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"俊和噚日新盤菁雋（TPlus）最細單位得128方呎，董事潘志才話設計參考學生宿舍，其實點止學生要住劏房，連巨企Google軟件工程師都要住埋一份！<br />\n<br />\n其實嚿年《Business Insider》報道已經報道過，Google加州一名當時23歲嘅軟件工程師Brandon S.，因為要慳租金同償還學費債務，於是花費約1萬美元，買了一架2006年福特貨車，內籠面積有128方呎，同俊和新盤菁雋面積最細但同可享皇帝式享受嘅劏房一樣咁大！<br />\n<br />\nBrandon當時話因為租房太貴，每月要2000美元，於是住喺貨車，每月固定成本只係121美元車保。佢話咁可以將90%稅後收入去還學生貸款同埋投資，仲可以有閒錢去啲靚餐廳食飯。<br />\n<br />\n俊和仲未公佈菁雋售價，但估計都至1萬元一呎起跳，各位學生哥，要比百幾二百萬買間宿舍，不如學吓Brandon，買架貨車仲實際！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20161202/19852759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852759&d=2iDFTzlNQyK5Og%2FdY0fH%2BAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=520071f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852759&h=6a98c5b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20161202/19852759</a>"},{"pid":"4c053dde32375841a556aa804279f32eab705b8a","tid":266128,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位學生哥，要比百幾二百萬買間宿舍，不如學吓Brandon，買架貨車仲實際！</blockquote><br />\n可能被多間港府部門檢控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20abc764100fc58f712e9fd982d8a05f6f1be527","tid":266128,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e31fcee5c9538beb2b455984647f9042445d0b","tid":266128,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,